---
name: add-api-endpoint
description: 添加新的API接口端点
---

# 添加新API端点的标准流程

## 1. 定义Pydantic Schema (backend/app/schemas/)

创建请求和响应模型：

```python
# schemas/your_module.py
from pydantic import BaseModel

class YourRequest(BaseModel):
    field1: str
    field2: int

class YourResponse(BaseModel):
    id: int
    data: str
    
    class Config:
        from_attributes = True
```

## 2. 创建Service业务逻辑 (backend/app/services/)

```python
# services/your_service.py
from sqlalchemy.orm import Session
from app.models import YourModel

def create_something(db: Session, data: dict):
    obj = YourModel(**data)
    db.add(obj)
    db.commit()
    db.refresh(obj)
    return obj
```

## 3. 添加API路由 (backend/app/api/v1/)

```python
# api/v1/your_route.py
from fastapi import APIRouter, Depends
from sqlalchemy.orm import Session
from app.database import get_db
from app.deps import get_current_user
from app.schemas.your_module import YourRequest, YourResponse
from app.services.your_service import create_something

router = APIRouter()

@router.post("/your-endpoint", response_model=YourResponse)
def create_endpoint(
    data: YourRequest,
    db: Session = Depends(get_db),
    current_user = Depends(get_current_user)
):
    result = create_something(db, data.dict())
    return result
```

## 4. 注册路由到主应用

在 `app/api/v1/router.py` 中引入并注册：

```python
from app.api.v1 import your_route

router.include_router(your_route.router, prefix="/your-module", tags=["Your Module"])
```

## 5. 前端API封装 (frontend/src/api/)

```typescript
// api/yourModule.ts
import client from './client'

export const createSomething = async (data: YourRequest) => {
  const response = await client.post('/api/v1/your-endpoint', data)
  return response.data
}
```

## 6. 测试

- 访问 http://localhost:8000/docs 测试API
- 使用前端调用验证
